{"tid":323942,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「好動李若彤」Kelly有信心　麥明詩撐「嫩版宋熙年」","createTime":"2017-07-16T05:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T07:45:47.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e93428ca0a98bafff52ce796437a9777e2f3fb7a","tid":323942,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498537058_12ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498537058_12ff.jpg&h=188b7486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(攝影：陳順禎)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498535973_95ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498535973_95ea.jpg&h=84a9f264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好動李若彤被指係今屆港姐大熱，佢就話自己都有摷番李若彤嘅相嚟睇。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498535975_bb78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498535975_bb78.jpg&h=32d66bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「好動李若彤」身邊嘅嫩版宋熙年Zoe，就有好友麥明詩撐。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498535977_698e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498535977_698e.jpg&h=ca832461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥明詩除咗有同Zoe(右二)食飯，原來亦有同今屆另一候選人Sophia(左二)食飯。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498535978_1fcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498535978_1fcc.jpg&h=babfef3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKelly上次第一次初選着黑色裙。(資料圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498535979_9e72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498535979_9e72.jpg&h=80ef8fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKelly真係好好動。(網上圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498535980_1ecb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498535980_1ecb.jpg&h=91b53338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKelly騎馬又騎大象。(網上圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498535981_58c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498535981_58c7.jpg&h=add66965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Kelly 網上圖片)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170627/56881459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170627%2F56881459&d=LQWQmKbjtdkBJpbj%2B%2FgmgI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=db72f94b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170627%2F56881459&h=371d1303\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170627/56881459</a>"},{"pid":"18110302f898094440181fd43d44afd03e153dae","tid":323942,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"排牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610551722d7d290c1b3c6d79214e90680b52c97e","tid":323942,"uid":70800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"大熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6ad1b4c4adef443ab2f7705ce2f6825f00adb1","tid":323942,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"個嘴好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8e4ea2c0be745d99acae9b0972dbd12e1c60c1","tid":323942,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"邊到似李若彤，似阿旦多啲"},{"pid":"139c3858eda02e934295ea1716ced2a3fb8e09bd","tid":323942,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"唔似宋熙年，似松井珠理奈"}]}